{
  "texts": [
    "After all the required images have been captured, they are sent to the image preprocessing stage to be adjusted before use.",
    "If the collected images do not fulfill the processing requirements, there is a need to employ image-enhancing methods (Basavaiah and Anthony, 2020).",
    "For an accurate disease classification, the image acquisition phase is crucial.",
    "The efficiency of the entire framework is highly dependent on the images acquired.",
    "ML models are trained on these images (Camargo and Smith, 2009)."
  ]
}